<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٣٤١ - قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1243">‌الْحَارِثُ بْنُ مِسْكِينٍ </a>قِرَاءَةً عَلَيْهِ وَأَنَا أَسْمَعُ: عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3383">‌ابْنِ الْقَاسِمِ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">‌مَالِكٌ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5917">‌</a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٩٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ابْنِ شِهَابٍ ، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">‌عَائِشَةَ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1565">‌وَحَفْصَةَ - </a>مِثْلَهُ: <span class="c2">«لَا يَصُومُ إِلَّا مَنْ أَجْمَعَ الصِّيَامَ قَبْلَ الْفَجْرِ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>